title: Van Zandt County, Texas
place_detail: Rustic Getaway at Mill Creek Ranch Resort
full_description: SOUTHERN DREAM is a brand new, luxurious, pond-side treehouse in the woods.  It is the ideal place to spend your honeymoon or a romantic getaway with your love.  Indoors, SOUTHERN DREAM has massive picture windows, a large walk-in rain shower, a fully stocked kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Outside, you’ll enjoy relaxing in the hot tub, resting on the swing bed, walking the trails, or fishing at the pond.  Make SOUTHERN DREAM your own and fall in love all over again.

title: Ravenna, Florida
full_description: BEAUTIFUL COZY CABIN FOR YOUR FAMILY!!! This beautifully decorated 700 sq ft. cabin has everything you need for your perfect getaway. Just a 45 minute drive north of McKinney located on 2.5 acres. You can sit back and enjoy the view of the trees while rocking of the front porch with your morning coffee. Located only 10 miles from Lake Bonham, this cabin has a full kitchen equipped with everything you need for a country escape

title: Pottsboro, San Antonio
place_detail: Lazy Acres Farmhouse. Peace. Beauty. Relaxation.
full_description: Our Kabanas are waterfront, single-room tiny homes with stunning lake views. Each Kabana is equipped with a queen bed, small fridge, Bluetooth speaker, indoor/outdoor seating, super unique fire-pit, and an outdoor kitchen complete with a BBQ grill. The AC unit will keep you chilly in the summer and warm in the winter and the electrical includes USB charging stations. Linens are provided for the beds and the bathroom and shower facilities are a short walk away

title: Cross Roads, California
full_description: Our Denton County country guest house which is located in the heart of the DFW Metroplex…approximately 40 miles northwest of downtown Dallas, 40 miles northeast of downtown Fort Worth and 60 miles from Arlington. You will have access to the home and private heated pool.

title: Anna, Utah
place_detail: Modern ranch cabin at the base of the mountains!
full_description: Long or short term rental. This cutie of a farm house was built in 1841 and is one of the oldest homes in Collin County.  Wrap around covered porch with a swing to watch the sunset or  overlook the 40 plus acres of rolling meadows and trees surrounding the home.  You could possibly spot some deer, wild turkey, or hear the coyotes howl at the full moon.  This home is very close to wedding venues, Hurricane Creek Country Club, and a short drive to downtown McKinney

title: Yantis, Tampa
full_description: The Rustic Getaway is located in one of the more private areas at Mill Creek Ranch Resort with a wooden, rustic interior. The bedroom offers a queen size bed and a TV, the living room area has a full size sleeper sofa with a TV and the 3 ft tall loft offers two twin size beds with a TV as well. This cottage also features a full kitchen, private bathroom and a washer/dryer. The outdoor amenities include a stone fire pit with chairs, a barbecue grill and an extended deck with furniture. The unique location of this cottage comes with a view of one of our ponds for catch and release fishing. The kids will love the Wii game console and games provided in the cottage as well!
